        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            <strong>The what:</strong> President Trump imposed a 50% tariff on
            Brazil to address its policies harming US companies, foreign policy,
            and the economy. He accused Brazil of demanding content moderation
            and user data under threat of penalty. He also condemned the
            prosecution of former Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro and imposed
            sanctions on the Brazilian Supreme Court Judge (<a
              style="
                text-decoration: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #06266d;
                color: black;
              "
