              target="_blank"
              >fact sheet</a
            >).
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            <strong>The why:</strong> Trump asserts that these tariffs are a
            retaliation for the
            <a
              style="
                text-decoration: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #06266d;
                color: black;
              "
              href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-1-aug-25-spotlight-h1-2-prosecution-of-jair-bolsonaro?source=website"
              target="_blank"
              >prosecution of Jair Bolsonaro</a
            >, his ally. Bolsonaro denies the assertions of a 2022 coup attempt
            but acknowledges attempting to reverse the election results. The US
            president also condemned the Brazilian Supreme Court judgeâ€™s orders
            to shut down Bolsonaroâ€™s social media account for spreading
            disinformation.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            <strong>The reaction:</strong> Brazil has
            <a
              style="
                text-decoration: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #06266d;
                color: black;
              "
              href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-1-aug-25-spotlight-h1-3-criticized-the-sanctions?source=website"
              target="_blank"
              >criticized the sanctions</a
            >
            on the judge and condemned the US for interfering in its justice
            system. The Brazilian Treasury Secretary said the political motives
            behind the tariffs undermine national sovereignty and the historical
            relationship between the two countries.
          </p>
